Teofilo Marzuach PLUMEY, Plaintiff, Appellant, v. Carolina Amelia ACOSTA et al., Defendants, Appellees. Circuit Court of Appeals, First Circuit. November 10, 1928. No. 2296. Francis H. Dexter and Mariano Acosta Velarde, both of San Juan, Porto Rico, for appellee.

Before BINGHAM, JOHNSON, and ANDERSON, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Dismissed for want of prosecution.
